{"tid":2111489,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"被人認錯但同時自己都唔sure對方係咪真係認錯, 自己都差啲認錯對方下嘅情況下應該點做好?","createTime":"2020-07-16T14:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T10:49:51.000Z","uid":251349,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3abcf18f54d0829ae2becefdb541590ffa37b8","tid":2111489,"uid":251349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有次上lecture被坐後面個靚女姐姐拍膊頭，問＂依~乜你又有讀呢科嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＂，我望咗一望佢個樣，幾似我一個以前返part time嘅同事，但又唔肯定係咪真係，同埋我又唔記得嗰個同事嘅名，咁我跟住就開始dilemma喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我心入面好似玩gal game 咁option A , option B, option C 去分析緊幾種回應手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n第一種應對方法，反問佢係咪認錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呢種應對手法十分絕情。<br />\ncase I:如果對方真係我個舊同事，我咁做好似特登扮唔識佢，又或者平時我冇擺佢在我眼內。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ncase II:而如果佢唔係我舊同事，到時又搞到佢好似大庭廣眾下認錯人出丑尷尬，我呢啲gentleman又唔想做到咁絕，所以呢個方案我否決咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二種應對方法，直接認定佢就係我之前個同事，並以此展開交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。呢種應對手法第一眼睇落十分自然，可以利落地進行對話交接，其他在場嘅人又唔會太在意（當場話佢認錯人會惹起其他人嘅關注同視線）<br />\ncase I:<br />\n而如果佢真係我舊同事，但我又叫唔出佢個名，咁又好似好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（明明人哋認得自己）。<br />\n<br />\ncase II:<br />\n但如果萬一佢實際上唔係我認識嘅同事，咁之後上堂又會好老尷，因為大家都認錯人（事實上嗰陣仲要係係啱啱開sem第一堂）。所以如果認定佢係舊同事，好似都冇好下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三種應對方法，沉默，等對方意識到認錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\ncase I:<br />\n如果對方真係我個舊同事，我咁做都係好似特登扮唔識佢，或者唔想show 佢，搞到我好似好無情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncase II:<br />\n而如果佢唔係我舊同事，咁又有兩種結局。結局A：佢都係意識唔到自己認錯人，跟住佢好再搭多幾句，我又會睇落好似好無情嘅人唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。結局B：佢意識到認錯人，咁就Happy Ending 大家相安無事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四種應對方法，喺冇指認佢係舊同事下展開交流。一種無論case I定II 都好似冇太大問題嘅做法，但事實上十分取決溝通技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為你唔知點樣可以做到完美地交流（唔知有咩可以講而唔暴露自己其實唔太認得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。<br />\n<br />\n最終，機智如我嘅小弟揀咗第3個option沉默<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為始終都有50%機會有happy ending，死就死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後結果就係佢繼續同我講嘢（之後佢講嘅嘢畀我知道佢真係認錯人，而我真係唔識佢，佢亦唔係我舊同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），而佢好似仲係意識唔到自己認錯人咁，咁呢個時候我就開始暗示佢認錯人喇，始終佢都幾影響我上堂（雖然第一堂都冇咩好上）<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋小弟毒Ｌ一個，咁樣被靚女姐姐chur 住，面都紅晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。點知我暗示完佢之後，佢開始眼淚凝眶想喊咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後真係喊咗出嚟，又話咩＂你以前唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＂，＂真係有咗第二個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＂，＂始亂終棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＂，＂大話連篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />＂，仲愈喊愈大聲。小弟嗰陣都想喊出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，小弟我一個A0小毒L，手仔都未掂過，就咁樣俾人憑空污人清白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後聽其他人都開始起閧，話咩前日見過我同其他女仔一齊偷偷地入時鐘酒店，佢哋都癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。最後我心灰灰咁走咗出去，嗰科我都drop Q咗。<br />\n<br />\n想問各位下次遇到啲咁嘅情況應該點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..."},{"pid":"82ccb492778f8508213ac2d138659d77bd0cbf67","tid":2111489,"uid":307114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7011a0c685c8b79da2314717b7471ae92552f443","tid":2111489,"uid":251349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:09:20.000Z","msg":"利申:真人真事，下次應該點做先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f78bbb7b3a2890d3f9568932275b5a276e8f4e","tid":2111489,"uid":300630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:14:16.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"8a8df619a34b24a36d6ddb17e3e0fb765e281dd9","tid":2111489,"uid":299433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"睇前半part仲以為係認真討論post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc7e0eb7305c57bf921b603252099ca53cf45a5","tid":2111489,"uid":251349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8df619a34b24a36d6ddb17e3e0fb765e281dd9","tid":2111489,"uid":299433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"睇前半part仲以為係認真討論post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:32:42.000Z","msg":"就係認真post嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba4840ab335d59e41a4c5edcacef8e179422346","tid":2111489,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"10/10<br />\n校園台好耐冇高質post"},{"pid":"7fd0b768aa4f813390dfeb6b6c04d19ee38fccf0","tid":2111489,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"排版問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇左幾隻字就唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><